graph TD
    User[User / Admin] -->|HTTPS| UI[React Admin UI]
    User -->|HTTPS| API[API Gateway / NestJS]
    
    UI -->|REST/WS| API
    
    subgraph Backend
        API --> Auth[Auth Module]
        API --> Masters[Masters Module]
        API --> Slaves[Slaves Module]
        API --> Copy[Copy Engine]
        
        Copy -->|Read| DB[(PostgreSQL)]
        Copy -->|Publish| MQ[RabbitMQ]
        Copy -->|Cache| Redis[(Redis)]
        
        Worker[Worker Service] -->|Consume| MQ
        Worker -->|Execute| Adapter[Broker Adapter]
    end
    
    subgraph External
        Adapter -->|API| Binance[Binance]
        Adapter -->|API| MT4[MetaTrader 4]
    end
